title Stealth Escape - Game Flow

[*] --> MainMenu
MainMenu --> FirstLevel : Play
FirstLevel --> Pause : P / Esc
Pause --> FirstLevel : P / Esc / Click
FirstLevel --> GameOver : Caught by hazard
GameOver --> FirstLevel : Enter / Space / Click
FirstLevel --> Win : All items + exit reached
Win --> [*] : Enter / Esc / Click

@enduml
